features: 【Portable Washing Machine】Turbine Washing Machine is perfect for travel and carry.It is safe, non-, and tasteless. It can be folded 20,000 times without breaking after experimental testing. 4 layers of sealing protection, all corners are comprehensive protection, easy to use, IP68 waterproof, you can use it with confidence.

【Leakage Protection Switch】Portable washing machine is widely used in various situations, using leakage protection switch, safe and harmless.Avoid secondary pollution to clothing, reduce odor and degrade trace organic matter, and easily deal with sensitive skin.

【Ultrasonic Cleaning】Mini washing machines have High-frequency vibration cavitation that accelerates the dispersion and emulsification of liquids and stains to achieve the purpose of cleaning. Hand rubbing and tumbling washing, conical water flowing, efficient cleaning, and care for clothes, to meet your various need. Avoid secondary pollution to clothing, reduce odor and degrade trace organic matter, and easily deal with sensitive skin.

【Wide Application】The compact turbo washing machine is easy and comfortable to use and does not take up space. Any bucket, washbasin, sink can be used for laundry. Perfect for children's clothing, underwear, socks, towels and more. In addition to washing clothes, it is also very suitable for washing small items such as jewelry, glasses, and fruits.

【4 Modes】Install the washing machine to the bottom or of a suitable bucket or sink, add your personal clothing to the bucket and add water, then power on and start washing. There are four different cleaning modes for you to choose from. Quick wash (5 minutes), mixing wash (8 minutes), scrub wash (10 minutes), power wash (15 minutes). and the frequency is 50/60Hz, low noise, easy to carry, which is the perfect choice for outdoor, travel.
